text: KSMJ-LP (100.9 FM) is a low-power FM radio station licensed to Edmond, Oklahoma, United States. The station is currently owned by Oklahoma Fellowship Of Catholic Men. ==History== The station call sign KSMJ-LP on February 21, 2014. ==References== ==External links== * * http://www.okcr.org/ SMJ-LP SMJ-LP Category:Religious radio stations in the United States Category:Radio stations established in 2016 Category:2016 establishments in Oklahoma SMJ-LP
